                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Williams</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Uhl</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-11-29">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 29, 1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Trial of Sanguily commenced yesterday noon; adjourned at 5 o’clock; resumed
                    to-day noon and finished at 3 o’clock. I attended as spectator in compliance
                    with instructions of Department. His advocate, Viondi, has made a magnificient
                    defense. Verdict not rendered yet.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
